</taxonomicName>
has been found in ditches, ponds (densely vegetated), marshes, lakes, lagoons (densely vegetated), and in quiet edges of streams and rivers (
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B190FFEBB10A3FEA0" author="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L." box="[835,1212,295,321]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="71 - 74" refId="ref45568" refString="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L. (1999) Relevamiento de la fauna de Belostomatidae en la provincia de Corrientes. Facena, 14, 71 - 74. [1998]" type="journal article" year="1999">Armúa de Reyes &amp; Estévez 1999</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B1E8BFEBB14E9FE84" author="Armua de Reyes, C. A. &amp; Estevez, A. L. &amp; Schnack, J. A." pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="37 - 42" refId="ref45720" refString="Armua de Reyes, C. A., Estevez, A. L. &amp; Schnack, J. A. (2006) Description of the preimaginal instars and redescription of the adult stage of Belostoma elongatum Montandon (Hemiptera: Belostomatidae). Zootaxa, 1175 (1), 37 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 1175.1.3" type="journal article" year="2006">
Armúa de Reyes 
<emphasis id="6DABEA83FFA40D2B1FC4FEBB14ABFE84" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="476">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B1B4CFED71639FE84" author="Poi de Neiff, A. &amp; Neiff, J. J." box="[256,550,331,357]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="220 - 225" refId="ref56262" refString="Poi de Neiff, A. &amp; Neiff, J. J. (2006) Riqueza de especies y similaridad de los invertebrados que viven en plantas flotantes de la planicie de inundacion del Rio Parana (Argentina). Interciencia, 31, 220 - 225." type="journal article" year="2006">Poi de Neiff &amp; Neiff 2006</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B187DFED716D9FE84" author="Ribeiro, J. R. I." box="[561,710,331,357]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="1 - 70" refId="ref56914" refString="Ribeiro, J. R. I. (2007) A review of the species of Belostoma Latreille, 1807 (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Belostomatidae) from the four southeastern Brazilian states. Zootaxa, 1477 (1), 1 - 70." type="journal article" year="2007">Ribeiro 2007</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B1883FED7103AFE84" author="Armua de Reyes, C. &amp; Kehr, A. I." box="[719,1061,331,357]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="355 - 366" refId="ref45789" refString="Armua de Reyes, C. &amp; Kehr, A. I. (2008) Ecologia de comunidades: diversidad, asociaciones y covariaciones interespecificas entre las especies del genero Belostoma en ambientes acuaticos de la provincia de Corrientes. Instituto Superior de Correlacion Geologica, Miscelanea INSUGEO, 17, 355 - 366." type="journal article" year="2008">Armúa de Reyes &amp; Kehr 2008</bibRefCitation>
). This species has also been taken at lights (
<bibRefCitation id="3B4E4B60FFA40D2B1AB3FEF315C5FE68" author="Almeida, T. M. de &amp; Stefanello, F. &amp; Hamada, N." box="[255,474,367,393]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476" pagination="20195906" refId="ref45152" refString="Almeida, T. M. de, Stefanello, F. &amp; Hamada, N. (2019) Belostomatidae (Heteroptera: Nepomorpha) held in the invertebrate collection of the Instituto Nacional de Pesquisas da Amazonia, Manaus, Brazil: inventory and new distributional records. Papeis Avulsos de Zoologia, 59, e 20195906. https: // doi. org / 10.11606 / 1807 - 0205 / 2019.59.06" type="journal article" year="2019">
Almeida 
<emphasis id="6DABEA83FFA40D2B1B2AFEF31583FE68" box="[358,412,367,393]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="476">et al.</emphasis>
2019
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5F603691FFA40D2B1A8BFE0F150BFDDC" blockId="25.[151,1437,150,573]" pageId="25" pageNumber="476">
At the INR, specimens were collected from the margins of the Iberá Lagoon (Estévez &amp; Armúa de Reyes 2003; Estévez 
<emphasis id="6DABEA83FFA40D2B1AB8FE2B1533FE30" box="[244,300,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="476">et al.</emphasis>
2003). During the present study, specimens were collected from the margins with dense floating, emergent, and submerged vegetation in unshaded lentic habitats (Fernández Lagoon, Medina Lagoon and Trin Lagoon), and in standing water of lotic habitats. It was also collected at the margins of a shaded roadside ditch without aquatic vegetation.
</paragraph>
